Great Bend BCCC DMR Repeater This repeater is a Moto MTR2000 running MMDVM and a open repeater connected to the Brandmeister Network. We have CKRG (TG31204), and Local (using TG9) on Time Slot 1. Central KS Skywarn (TG31206) on Time Slot 2. Cluster (Pawnee Rock, Great Bend, Russell Hosp, Russell, and Hays) TG 2 on Time Slot 2. Please Use TS 2 for all other Brandmeister TG
